OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FLife-saving allergy pens will be
OL,7,Fstored in all UK schools from
OL,8,FSeptember after a campaign in memory
OL,9,Fof a five-year-old boy who died from a
OL,10,Freaction to cow's milk.
OL,12,FThe move is among new statutory
OL,13,Fguidance for schools, called
OL,14,FBenedict's Law, which will also
OL,15,Fprovide training for teachers to
OL,16,Fensure they can act quickly in case of
OL,17,Femergencies.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
