OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FThe nationwide requirements come after
OL,7,Fa campaign by the National Allergy
OL,8,FStrategy Group and families including
OL,9,FHelen and Peter Blythe.
OL,11,FTheir son Benedict, from Stamford in
OL,12,FLincolnshire, lost his life after a
OL,13,Freaction at school in 2021.
OL,15,FSchools will also be expected to have
OL,16,Fclear allergy policies and healthcare
OL,17,Fplans, the Department for Education
OL,18,F(DfE) said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FHelen Blythe, co-founder of the
OL,7,FBenedict Blythe Foundation, said:
OL,8,F"This week marks a historic turning
OL,9,Fpoint for children with allergies and
OL,10,Ftheir families.
OL,12,F"For too long, whether a child was
OL,13,Fsafe at school depended on where they
OL,14,Fhappened to go.
OL,16,F"From September, schools across
OL,17,FEngland will have clear national
OL,18,Fexpectations on how they keep children
OL,19,Fwith allergies safe."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FShe added: "We are incredibly proud
OL,7,Fthat Benedict's legacy will help
OL,8,Fprotect generations of children to
OL,9,Fcome."
OL,11,FBenedict died after accidental
OL,12,Fexposure to cow's milk protein at
OL,13,FBarnack Primary School, between
OL,14,FStamford and Peterborough, in December
OL,15,F2021.
OL,26,@nD@LOUqD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FAn inquest found the school did not
OL,7,Ffollow all the measures in place to
OL,8,Fprevent the fatal anaphylactic
OL,9,Freaction, and that there were risks of
OL,10,Fcontamination and delays in
OL,11,Fadministering an adrenaline pen.
OL,13,FA prevention of future deaths report
OL,14,Fsaid initial investigations into
OL,15,FBenedict's death focused on him having
OL,16,Featen a McVitie's biscuit that he had
OL,17,Fbrought in from home on the day he
OL,18,Fcollapsed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FIt later became clear the biscuit did
OL,7,Fnot cause Benedict's anaphylactic
OL,8,Freaction, and an inquest found he had
OL,9,Fprobably been given cow's milk protein
OL,10,Fin his bottle during break time.
OL,12,FIn the report, coroner Elizabeth Gray
OL,13,Fsaid the failure to retain Benedict's
OL,14,Fvomit or preserve evidence at the
OL,15,Fscene meant samples could not be
OL,16,Ftested, which could have helped to
OL,17,Fidentify what caused Benedict's
OL,18,Freaction at an earlier stage.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FEducation minister Olivia Bailey
OL,7,Fpraised the Blythes' campaign, saying:
OL,8,F"Benedict's Law means every single
OL,9,Fschool will now have the training
OL,10,Fplans and the life-saving equipment in
OL,11,Fplace to protect every child.
OL,13,F"That's all thanks to the
OL,14,Fdetermination of Helen and Peter
OL,15,FBlythe, who turned unimaginable
OL,16,Ftragedy into a legacy that will
OL,17,Fprotect children for generations to
OL,18,Fcome."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,7,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, welcomed
OL,8,Fthe new guidance, but said schools
OL,9,Fneeded funding to make sure they had
OL,10,Fthe staffing capacity needed.
OL,12,F"While guidance for schools is
OL,13,Fcrucial, equally important is access
OL,14,Fto the right resources, including
OL,15,Fsufficient staffing capacity in the
OL,16,Fschool to deliver their duties, and
OL,17,Falways ensuring access to specialist
OL,18,Fhealth support for pupils whose
OL,19,Fconditions require genuine expertise
OL,20,Fto keep them healthy and safe," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@tD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,F"Each of these things require funding
OL,7,Fto implement and schools cannot be
OL,8,Fexpected to fund them from their
OL,9,Fexisting constrained budgets.
OL,11,F"Expecting schools to stock 'spare'
OL,12,Fadrenaline auto-injectors for use in
OL,13,Femergency situations appears a
OL,14,Fsensible step, as is training staff to
OL,15,Fuse them effectively.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783680590
OL,3,CAll schools to stock allergy pens
OL,4,Cafter boy's death
OL,6,F"However, the Government needs to be
OL,7,Fconfident that there are sufficient
OL,8,Fstocks maintained across the country
OL,9,Fto ensure each setting can keep a
OL,10,Fsufficient share of adrenaline auto-
OL,11,Finjectors."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]
